'''他'''（英语：'''Him'''），是为[[同性戀|同性恋]]观众制作的[[色情片|色情电影]]。

==简介==
电影集中在一个年轻的同性恋者与[[耶稣|耶稣基督]]的生活中发展色情关系。这部电影几乎无人所知，直到1979年，在书籍《金色土耳其奖》中出现，在书中被称为“最色情的色情学说。”<ref>{{cite book|title=The Golden Turkey Awards: Nominees and Winners, The Worst Achievements in Hollywood History|last=Medved|first=Harry|author2=Michael Medved|year=1980|publisher=Perigree Book|location=NY|page=122}}</ref>

==遗失==
在书籍中，并没有找到该电影。它被在线杂志《Film Threat》称为最抢手的[[散失电影|散失电影]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Film Threat's Top 10 Lost Films, Part 4|url=http://www.filmthreat.com/features/1899|accessdate=16 November 2014|author=Hall, Phil|date=March 1, 2007|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150217005822/http://www.filmthreat.com/features/1899|archivedate=2015-02-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>  

部分网站认为该电影是个骗局，但是《Screw magazine》《Variety》和《The Village Voice》对该电影的评论被找到，<ref name="obscurity">{{cite web|title=Lost Movie Detective: Him|url=http://obscurityandbeyond.blogspot.com/2010/02/lost-movie-detective-him-1974.html|accessdate=3 March 2010|date=February 11, 2010|work=To Obscurity and Beyond...|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112033015/http://obscurityandbeyond.blogspot.com/2010/02/lost-movie-detective-him-1974.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=HIM, Reviewed by Al Goldstein|url=http://mesmerize.proboards.com/index.cgi?board=entertainment&action=display&thread=2399|accessdate=3 March 2010|author=Anderson, Billy A.|date=December 16, 2005|work=Mesmerize|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715114748/http://mesmerize.proboards.com/index.cgi?board=entertainment&action=display&thread=2399|archivedate=2011-07-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>几份报纸广告提及该电影在纽约戏剧播放。<ref name=obscurity/><ref>{{Cite web|title=FilmChat: The gay Jesus movie -- hoax, or fact?|url=http://filmchatblog.blogspot.com/2005/05/gay-jesus-movie-hoax-or-fact.html|accessdate=2019-10-13|work=filmchatblog.blogspot.com|archive-date=2019-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913150440/http://filmchatblog.blogspot.com/2005/05/gay-jesus-movie-hoax-or-fact.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

这部电影可能是最近的遗失电影。

